javatex

Class LaTeXSnippet

  • java.lang.Object
    • javatex.LaTeXSnippet
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    TeX
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    LaTeXDocument, LaTeXPackage

    public abstract class LaTeXSnippet
extends java.lang.Object
implements TeX
    Represents a snippet of LaTeX code. When a list of LaTeXSnippets are combined and saved as a .tex file, that resulting file should always be a valid snippet. By that logic, any individual LaTeXSnippet should also be valid when enclosed in the correct headers and footers.
    Version:
    2020-10-25
    Author:
    Keith Allatt
